sentence: In early trading on Friday, shares of Goldman Sachs Group topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 2.2%.
Year to date, Goldman Sachs Group registers a 20.3% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Walgreens Boots Alliance, trading down 4.0%.
Walgreens Boots Alliance is showing a gain of 0.1% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Home Depot, trading down 0.4%, and UnitedHealth Group, trading up 2.0% on the day.
